{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/personalblog/2007_04_01_archives.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\"\r\n\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Arthur Asuncion's Official Site: Blog</title>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n<!--\r\n.normalFont {font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif}\r\n.header {font-size: xx-large; color: #000088 }\r\n.footer {font-size: x-small}\r\n.post {  margin:.5em 0 1.5em;\r\n  border-bottom:1px solid #888888;\r\n  padding-bottom:0.4em;\r\n}\r\n.small {font-size: small; }\r\n-->\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<table width=\"70%\"  border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"15\" cellspacing=\"4\" bordercolor=\"#005588\" align=\"center\" >\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"75%\" height=\"110\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"normalFont\"><span class=\"header\"><a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion\">Arthur Asuncion</a></span>       \r\n\t<br>\r\n\t<br>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/research.htm\"><img src=\"researchIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/cv.htm\"><img src=\"cvIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/ics.htm\"><img src=\"computerIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/blog.htm\"><img src=\"blogIconSmall.gif\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/faith.htm\"><img src=\"crossIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/articles.htm\"><img src=\"articleIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/music.htm\"><img src=\"guitarIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>--<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/origins.htm\"><img src=\"originsIconSmall.jpg\" width=25 height=25 align=\"absmiddle\" border=0 /></a>\r\n\t<br><br>\t\r\n\t<strong>Personal Blog</strong></td>\r\n    <td width=\"25%\" height=\"110\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><a href=\"http://www.blogger.com\"><img src=\"blogIcon.gif\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\" align=\"middle\" border=0 /></a></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\r\n    <td height=\"164\" class=\"normalFont\">\r\n\t\r\n\t<p><span class=\"small\">Monday, April 16, 2007\r\n          <!-- Begin .post -->\r\n    </span> </p>\r\n      <div class=\"post\"><a name=\"1812449949971595768\"></a>\r\n        <h3> <a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/personalblog/2007_04_01_archives.htm#1812449949971595768\" title=\"permanent link\"> Virginia Tech: There is Hope </a> </h3>\r\n        \r\n          <div class=\"post-body\">\r\n            <div class=\"small\"><div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>I cannot imagine the anguish and confusion that the Virginia Tech community is feeling right now.   Please take a moment to pray for the victims' families and friends.  This incident is a poignant reminder to all of us of the fragility of human life, and the depths of depravity that a human heart can achieve.  In days as dark and hellish as this one, it is vital for all of us to lay hold of the only eternal hope -- the <a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Easuncion/peace.htm\">hope of heaven</a>.<br /><br />There is a Book that we can turn to in times of trouble.  Here are some verses:<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Jhn/Jhn011.html#25\">Jhn 11:25</a> -- Jesus said unto her, <span class=\"SrptH\">I am</span> the resurrection, and <span class=\"SrptH\">the life</span>: <span class=\"SrptH\">he that</span> believeth in me, though he were dead, yet shall he live:<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Mat/Mat011.html#28\">Mat 11:28</a> -- <span class=\"SrptH\">Come</span> unto me, <span class=\"SrptH\">all</span> [ye] that labour and are heavy laden, <span class=\"SrptH\">and I</span> will give you rest.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Psa/Psa090.html#12\">Psa 90:12</a> -- <span class=\"SrptH\">So</span> teach [us] to number our days, <span class=\"SrptH\">that</span> we may <span class=\"SrptH\">apply [our] hearts</span> unto wisdom.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Mat/Mat005.html#4\">Mat 5:4</a> -- Blessed [are] they that mourn: for they shall be comforted.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Psa/Psa046.html#1\">Psa 46:1</a> -- God [is] our <span class=\"SrptH\">refuge</span> and strength, <span class=\"SrptH\">a very</span> present help in trouble.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Mat/Mat016.html#26\">Mat 16:26</a> -- For <span class=\"SrptH\">what is</span> a man profited, if he shall <span class=\"SrptH\">gain</span> the whole world, and lose his own soul? <span class=\"SrptH\">or</span> what shall a man give in exchange for his soul?<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/Rev/Rev021.html#4\">Rev 21:4</a> -- And <span class=\"SrptH\">God shall</span> wipe away all tears from their eyes; and there shall be <span class=\"SrptH\">no</span> more death, <span class=\"SrptH\">neither sorrow</span>, nor crying, neither shall there be any more pain: for <span class=\"SrptH\">the former</span> things are passed away.<div style=\"clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em\"></div></div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <p class=\"footer\"><a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/personalblog/2007_04_01_archives.htm#1812449949971595768\" title=\"permanent link\">11:30 PM</a> \r\n\t\t    </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <!-- End .post -->\r\n      <!-- Begin #comments -->\r\n      \r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\t<p><span class=\"small\">Tuesday, April 03, 2007\r\n          <!-- Begin .post -->\r\n    </span> </p>\r\n      <div class=\"post\"><a name=\"117566909044824152\"></a>\r\n        <h3> <a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/personalblog/2007_04_01_archives.htm#117566909044824152\" title=\"permanent link\"> Ping Pong in Bren Hall? </a> </h3>\r\n        \r\n          <div class=\"post-body\">\r\n            <div class=\"small\"><div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>I heard that Bren Hall may have a student lounge with a ping-pong table.  This is welcome news, since table tennis is one of my favorite activities.  I used to play a lot of table tennis in high school, and I even competed in some tournaments (USATT rating ~ 1550).  Table tennis as a sport is actually quite difficult, since the ball moves so fast and since there are a variety of spins that you need to be able to react to within a split second.  Playing became really fun when I learned how to serve well and how to attack the ball with a topspin loop.  Watch this <a href=\"http://tt.mainstreet.net/markkent/HuangKimHilite.MPG\">video clip</a> of a rally between two pros to see how fast the ball can move in a real game.  Whether one is a beginner or an expert, ping pong is fun to play and watch, and that's why I'm glad that they are puting up a table in Bren Hall.<div style=\"clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em\"></div></div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <p class=\"footer\"><a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~asuncion/personalblog/2007_04_01_archives.htm#117566909044824152\" title=\"permanent link\">8:28 PM</a> \r\n\t\t    </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <!-- End .post -->\r\n      <!-- Begin #comments -->\r\n      \r\n\t\r\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.blogger.com/static/v1/common/js/327583163-csitaillib.js\"></script>\n<script>if (typeof(window.attachCsiOnload) != 'undefined' && window.attachCsiOnload != null) { window.attachCsiOnload('ext_blogspot'); }</script>\r\n\t</td>\r\n\t<td width=\"25%\" class=\"normalFont 